HEADWORD: Shotten
<hw>Shot"ten</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Properly p. p. of
<ets>shoot</ets>; AS. <ets>scoten</ets>, <ets>sceoten</ets>, p. p. of
<ets>sce⟦oacute⟧tan</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having ejected the
