<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Shot out of its socket; dislocated, as a
bone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

